data.description: Look no more! Nestled on a sprawling 1-acre lot, this exquisite semi-custom home offers a harmonious blend of luxury, comfort, and picturesque natural beauty. A 4-car garage with a storage area and a welcoming front porch set the grand entrance. Discover a desirable great room where a cozy fireplace and 12-ft ceilings create a warm & inviting atmosphere! Abundant natural light enhances the ambiance, complemented by designer paint and a mix of tasteful flooring. The impeccable kitchen features SS appliances, granite counters, a center island, a walk-in pantry, coffee bar and ample cabinetry with crown molding. The office has french doors is versatile and ideal for an office or 2nd guest space! Each bedroom has its own walk-in closet, emphasizing the thoughtfully designed space. The main floor Primary Suite stands out with two walk-in closets and a 5 piece ensuite.  Completing the main level, you have a generously laundry room complete with a Coffee Bar and 2 undercounter Wine/Beverage fridges! You'll love the HUGE basement, where you can find a vast entertainment area equipped with a wet bar/kitchenette! The third bedroom and bathroom make this space perfect for guests or family members seeking their retreat. Additionally, there's 755 sqft of unfinished space, providing ample storage or the potential for future customization. Enjoy the expansive backyard with a covered patio - an excellent spot for al fresco dining, entertaining, or simply unwinding while enjoying the mountain views!  Want MORE? This property also includes a separate 600 sqft outbuilding fully wired with 220-volt electricity, insulated finished walls, and many built-in cabinets. Whether you're a DIY enthusiast or need extra storage, this space is a flexible bonus. A serene farmland stretches out behind the property, creating a sense of serenity and tranquility! This gem does not disappoint!
